snippet.title: NÜRNBERG Trailer German Deutsch (2026) Russell Crowe, Rami Malek
snippet.description:
Offizieller "Nürnberg" Trailer Deutsch German 2026 | Abonnieren ➤ https://abo.yt/kc | (OT: Nuremberg) Russell Crowe, Rami Malek Movie Trailer | Kino: 7 Mai 2026 | Filminfos https://KinoCheck.de/film/6kk/nuernberg-2026?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
Nürnberg, 1945. In den Ruinen einer vom Krieg gezeichneten Stadt erhält der US-amerikanische Psychiater Dr. Douglas M. Kelley den Auftrag, die inhaftierten Hauptverantwortlichen des NS-Regimes in Vorbereitung auf die Nürnberger Prozesse zu untersuchen. Unter ihnen ist auch der ehemalige Reichsmarschall Hermann Göring, dessen Intelligenz, Charisma und Gerissenheit Kelley zugleich herausfordern und faszinieren. Trotz anfänglicher Machtspiele gelingt es dem Arzt, Görings Vertrauen zu gewinnen und Einblick in seine Persönlichkeit zu erhalten. Während im Gerichtssaal die Verhandlungen beginnen, fällt es Kelley jedoch zunehmend schwerer, die notwendige Distanz zu seinem Klienten zu wahren.

snippet.title: Pre-Order Trailer | Marathon

Marathon releases March 5, 2026. 

Secrets. Buried and rotting. With the UESC holding the shovel.  
That's where you come in, Runner.

Scavenge the lost colony of Tau Ceti IV in the survival extraction FPS from the creators of Halo and Destiny.

Pre-order Marathon now: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3065800/Marathon/
PlayStation 5: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/marathon/

snippet.title: End Of Beginning - DJO
snippet.description:

⇨ Keep listening: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzPwICaYOEow9Ts4wjBop4j7dOUu2ULl
🌟 Escucha: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZ0hz9KHThgnFWgWswXFz9WGALfrLuXht

DJO:
https://youtube.com/@djomusic887?si=O3s0YU3ewNSArWJ3
https://www.instagram.com/djotime?igsh=MTk4cGx3eWZrdzBjaA==

🎤 Lyrics:
Just one more tear to cry, one teardrop from my eye
You better save it for
The middle of the night when things aren't black and white
Enter, Troubadour
"Remember twenty-four?"

[Chorus]
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning

[Verse 2]
This song has started now, and you're just finding out
Now isn't that a laugh?
A major sacrifice, but clueless at the time
Enter, Caroline
"Just trust me, you'll be fine"
And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye, goodbye)

You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the city, not the city out the man
You take the man out of the—

And when I'm back in Chicago, I feel it
Another version of me, I was in it
Oh, I wave goodbye to the end of beginning
(Goodbye, goodbye)

#endofbeginning #djo #asttro
